Package org.knime.base.node.viz.property.shape Description

Contains the Shape Manager and Shape Appender node to set shapes for a nominal column. Both nodes append a ShapeHandler instance to the input data for one particular column. For details see the ShapeManagerNodeFactory and ShapeAppenderNodeFactory factory classes.
